<DOCID> 25242 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 2, 1989, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part 6; Page 1; Column 3; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
