<P>
CALIFORNIA -- FEDERAL AID; WELFARE PROGRAMS -- CALIFORNIA; HEALTH CARE -- 
CALIFORNIA; UNITED STATES -- IMMIGRATION; UNITED STATES -- FINANCES; 
LEGISLATION -- UNITED STATES; AMNESTY 
</P>
